1199	
1200	    /* Create AudioContext early for decoding.
1201	       Browser autoplay policy: context starts in 'suspended' state.
1202	       decodeAudioData() is pure computation — works without resume().
1203	       Actual audio output requires audioCtx.resume() after user gesture
